i-list-ul\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Contents\\\"}]]}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"id\\\":\\\"city-hero\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-hero-section \\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"section-shell city-hero-shell\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-hero-copy\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-breadcrumbs\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Home\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Memphis\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-eyebrow\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Bluff City Dog Spots\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h1\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Dog Parks in Memphis, TN\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-chip-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-chip\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-label\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Verified Spots\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-value\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"16+\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-chip\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-label\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Avg Rating\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-value\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"4.3 / 5\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"With a focus on massive scale and natural beauty, Memphis offers a unique dog park experience that prioritizes freedom, exploration, and the great outdoors.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-rich-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Memphis, the \\\\\\\"Bluff City,\\\\\\\" is home to a dog park culture defined by its scale and appreciation for riverfront beauty. The jewel is \\\\\\\"The Outback\\\\\\\" at \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://memphisparks.com/park/shelby-farms-park/\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Shelby Farms Park\\\"}],null,\\\", a 100+ acre off-leash area with ponds and miles of trails. This space attracts visitors from across the Mid-South, creating a community who value exercise and exploration. Beyond Shelby Farms, the city maintains neighborhood runs like Overton Bark in Midtown, offering an intimate and shaded experience. For those navigating varied terrains, our \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/owner-resources\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"owner resources\\\"}],null,\\\" provide info on water safety and the best times to visit to enjoy Mississippi River breezes that cool the riverside runs during humid afternoons.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"The trend in Memphis is the revitalization of urban spaces into sustainable play areas reflecting the city’s creative spirit. We see growth in community-led initiatives and private enrichment-first daycare centers. These facilities incorporate adventure-play elements, such as climbing structures and scent-work courses, designed to give dogs a mental workout. Hygiene standards are being modernized, with more facilities adopting antimicrobial turf and hospital-grade sanitization to ensure a healthy environment. While Southern charm remains the foundation of its pet culture, these innovations ensure Memphis dogs have access to world-class care and diverse social opportunities. Whether seeking a trek through the Outback or a social session in Midtown, Memphis provides a canine infrastructure as expansive as the Mississippi and as soulful as its music.\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta primary\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"park-directory\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-list-check\\\"}],\\\"Browse directory\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta ghost\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"map-and-neighborhoods\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$L31\\\",\\\"Open map\\\"]}],\\\"$L32\\\"]}],\\\"$L33\\\"]}],\\\"$L34\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L35\\\",\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\",\\\"$L3f\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2b:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-new\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-grid\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h4\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"IndoorDogPark\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-links\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/about\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"About us\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/partners\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Partners\\\"}]}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",