g Park.  What makes this dog facility special is its safe, wonderful, great. they have improved the dog park and fenced in the area opening to the woods to keep our furry family pets safe… lots of snakes were reported in those woods awhile back Located in a safe area, This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (901) 385-6484. Visit their website at http://www.cityofbartlett.org/ to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"bartlett-dog-park\",\"address\":\"5220 Shelter Run Ln\",\"street\":\"5220 Shelter Run Ln\",\"city\":\"Memphis\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"38135\",\"full_address\":\"5220 Shelter Run Ln, Memphis, TN 38135, USA\",\"latitude\":35.26919660000001,\"longitude\":-89.8536463,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJYfg1ZNd5f4gR92LzlkHDikk\",\"phone\":\"(901) 385-6484\",\"website\":\"http://www.cityofbartlett.org/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.6,\"reviewCount\":121,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ-Q9Ahvudf4gR20M2a8NEC7c\",\"name\":\"Bartlett Pet Grooming\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Bartlett Pet Grooming.  What makes this dog facility special is its professional, clean, amazing. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners i